Text: I am so happy that you reached out! I am so so very proud of you seeking help. I have just found myself looking for help yet again- I am calling tomorrow for a therapist  myself. Just keep being honest the most horrid part of the eating disorder is the lies and secrets we hide from others and sometimes even ourselves! Stay strong!
